snippet.title: Tom & Jerry: The Ultimate Game of Cat and Mouse! [Nes][CompleteTheGame]
snippet.description:
Tom & Jerry: The Ultimate Game of Cat and Mouse!, or Tom and Jerry (and Tuffy) as it says ingame, is a good little platformer.
Reminds me of a Nes version of Cool Spot.
Graphically it is really good, especially the big sprites of Tom.
Did you see the Nes in one of the levels?
